"{\n  \"text\": \"Hey everybody, Scotty here, and I am giving a talk on composting this weekend, Sunday, at Plant Con 2024 here in Houston, Texas. It's gonna be about all things compost. It's gonna be awesome. I can't wait. It's not gonna be just about compost and how to make it, it's gonna be why you should be making it. I'm gonna do a uh kind of a deep dive into the beneficial aspects of the decay cycle, not just for your garden, not just for your soil, not just for your backyard and all these different things, but for your life itself. Anyway, uh come join me, PlantCon 2024. I'll be giving a speech Sunday at 4.15. Speech talk, whatever. And uh it's gonna be tons of fun. Please come out and it's gonna be all about compost. Good old-fashioned aerobic breakdown of garbage and leaves. Thanks, y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hey everybody, Scotty here, and I am giving a talk on composting this weekend, Sunday, at Plant Con 2024 here in Houston, Texas.\",\n      \"start\": 1.52,\n      \"end\": 10.32,\n      \"duration\": 8.8,\n      \"confidence\": 0.99,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" He\",\n          \"start\": 1.52,\n          \"end\": 1.84,\n          \"duration\": 0.32,\n          \"confidence\": 0.996\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"y\",\n          \"start\": 1.84,\n          \"end\": 1.92,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 2.0,\n          \"end\": 2.08,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"yb\",\n          \"start\": 2.08,\n          \"end\": 2.16,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"ody\",\n          \"start\": 2.16,\n          \"end\": 2.32,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \",\",\n